1. Install python
2. Install Synaptic
3. In synaptic, install:
   *ipython notebook
   *matplotlib
   *scipy
   *pandas
   *sympy
   *python setuptools
4. tornado 4.2 https://pypi.python.org/pypi/tornado
   tar xvzf tornado-$VERSION.tar.gz
   cd tornado-$VERSION
   python setup.py build
   sudo python setup.py install
5. jsonschema https://pypi.python.org/pypi/jsonschema#downloads
   same as installing tornado, run the setup.py file with python, build and then   install

6.Themes:
https://github.com/nsonnad/base16-ipython-notebook
